msgctxt "sn38.6:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 38 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 38 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn38.6:0.2"
msgid "1. Jambukhādakavagga "
msgstr "1. With Jambukhādaka "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 6. Paramassāsappattasutta → paramassāsasuttaṃ (bj) | paramassāso (pts1)
msgctxt "sn38.6:0.3"
msgid "6. Paramassāsappattasutta "
msgstr "6. Ultimate Solace "

# NOTE: he must have been to a Tony Robbins seminar.
#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.255, sc1
msgctxt "sn38.6:1.1"
msgid "“‘Paramassāsappatto, paramassāsappatto’ti, āvuso sāriputta, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Reverend Sāriputta, they speak of this thing called ‘gaining ultimate solace’. "

msgctxt "sn38.6:1.2"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, āvuso, paramassāsappatto hotī”ti? "
msgstr "At what point do you gain ultimate solace?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn38.6:1.3"
msgid "“Yato kho, āvuso, bhikkhu channaṃ phassāyatanānaṃ samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ viditvā anupādāvimutto hoti, ettāvatā kho, āvuso, paramassāsappatto hotī”ti. "
msgstr "“When a mendicant is freed by not grasping after truly understanding the six fields of contacts’ origin, ending, gratification, drawback, and escape, at that point they’ve gained ultimate solace.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn38.6:1.4"
msgid "“Atthi panāvuso, maggo atthi paṭipadā, etassa paramassāsassa sacchikiriyāyā”ti? "
msgstr "“But, reverend, is there a path and a practice for realizing this ultimate solace?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn38.6:1.5"
msgid "“Atthi kho, āvuso, maggo atthi paṭipadā, etassa paramassāsassa sacchikiriyāyā”ti. "
msgstr "“There is.” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn38.6:1.6"
msgid "“Katamo pana, āvuso, maggo katamā paṭipadā, etassa paramassāsassa sacchikiriyāyā”ti? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn38.6:1.7"
msgid "“Ayameva kho, āvuso, ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo etassa paramassāsassa sacchikiriyāya, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn38.6:1.8"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn38.6:1.9"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, āvuso, maggo ayaṃ paṭipadā, etassa paramassāsassa sacchikiriyāyā”ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn38.6:1.10"
msgid "“Bhaddako, āvuso, maggo bhaddikā paṭipadā, etassa paramassāsassa sacchikiriyāya. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn38.6:1.11"
msgid "Alañca panāvuso sāriputta, appamādāyā”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn38.6:1.12"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

